faqs.question: Can I cancel an appointment booked through online

alternateQuestions.question: Is there a way to cancel an appointment that I've booked online?
What's the procedure for canceling an appointment made through the online system?

faqs.label: Can I cancel an appointment booked through online

answer.text: Yes, please type “modify appointment” to cancel your confirmed appointment.

faqs.question: What are the time restrictions for canceling an appointment

alternateQuestions.question: Is there a specific notice period required for appointment cancellations?
How much advance notice is needed if I need to cancel my appointment?

faqs.label: What are the time restrictions for canceling an appointment

answer.text: You can cancel an appointment immediately following the booking of an appointment till a day prior to the appointment date.

faqs.question: Can I make an online booking with my credit card for somebody else

alternateQuestions.question: Can I make an online reservation for another person using my credit card?
Is there an option to pay for someone else's booking with my credit card through the online system?

faqs.label: Can I make an online booking with my credit card for somebody else

faqs.question: Can I make an online appointment and pay later

alternateQuestions.question: Can I make an appointment online now and settle the payment at a later time?
Am I allowed to secure an online appointment without immediate payment?

faqs.label: Can I make an online appointment and pay later

answer.text: We do not provide this facility now. Our aim is to assist you in obtaining a confirmed appointment with a doctor on a selected time slot and date.

faqs.question: Can I reschedule an online appointment

alternateQuestions.question: Can I request to reschedule my online appointment for a different time?
May I inquire about rescheduling options for my online appointment?
|| [ method rule system ] [ reschedule ] online appointment

faqs.label: Can I reschedule an online appointment

answer.text: Yes, you can reschedule an online appointment. Please type “Modify Appointment” to reschedule.May I inquire about rescheduling options for my online appointment?

alternateQuestions.question: Could you clarify what is meant by an onsite appointment?
I'm not familiar with onsite appointments; could you provide more details?

answer.text: When you visit a doctor and seek an appointment for a future date, this can be done at his location by making payment in cash. The booking charges in case of “onsite appointment” are less in comparison to the “online appointments” as we do not require to pay to the payment gateway provider in case of cash receipts.
